				<h3>The Three Triggers of Stroke</h3>
				
				<p>After reading tons of books, articles, and journals, I discovered a gem from the American Heart Association. It came to me as I was reading up on reversing heart disease for the LifeHeal program. It turns out the American Heart Association has made clear guidelines for stroke risk. </p>
				<p>I was surprised to learn that we are at a higher risk for a stroke when 3 specific biomarkers rise together. These 3 markers together, not 1, not 2, but when these 3 markers are up together your chance of stroke are elevated. </p>
